---
import ResourcePageLayout from "../../../layouts/ResourcePageLayout.astro";
---

<ResourcePageLayout
  title="eCash"
  description="Introduktion til eCash — digitale kontanter bygget på Bitcoin og Lightning."
  lang="da"
>
  <section class="nav-buttons">
    <a href="/da/laer-mere/lightning" class="nav-btn">Lightning-netværket</a>
    <a href="/da/laer-mere/liquid" class="nav-btn">Liquid</a>
    <a href="/da/laer-mere/bitcoin-blockchain" class="nav-btn">Bitcoin Blokkæden</a>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <p>
      eCash er digitale kontanter bygget oven på Bitcoin. Med Cashu-protokollen kan du sende og modtage bitcoin øjeblikkeligt, næsten gratis og med fuld privatliv – ligesom fysiske kontanter, men i digital form. Tokens lever på din enhed, og ingen kan spore dine transaktioner.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="category-section">
    <h2>eCash Wallets</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Vælg en wallet for at komme i gang med at bruge eCash.</p>
    <div class="links-grid">
      <a href="https://www.enuts.cash/" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">eNuts</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">iOS & Android</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://wallet.cashu.me/" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">Cashu.me</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">Web (PWA)</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://nutstash.app/" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">Nutstash</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">Web (PWA)</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.minibits.cash/" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">Minibits</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">Android</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="category-section">
    <h2>Mints & Værktøjer</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Find en mint at forbinde din wallet til. Du kan bruge flere mints for at sprede risikoen.</p>
    <div class="links-grid">
      <a href="https://cashumints.space/" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">CashuMints.space</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">Mint-oversigt</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://bitcoinmints.com/?tab=mints" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">Bitcoinmints.com</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">Mint-oversigt</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://proxnut.com/" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">Proxnut</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">Proxy for mints</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Hvordan virker eCash?</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">1</span>
        <div class="step-text">
          <strong>Indbetal bitcoin</strong> – Du sender bitcoin (typisk via Lightning) til en mint.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">2</span>
        <div class="step-text">
          <strong>Modtag eCash-tokens</strong> – Minten udsteder tokens ved hjælp af "blinde signaturer". Det betyder, at minten ikke kan se, hvem der ejer hvilke tokens.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">3</span>
        <div class="step-text">
          <strong>Brug dine tokens</strong> – Send dem til andre, betal for services, eller indløs dem til bitcoin igen. Transaktioner er øjeblikkelige og næsten gratis.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Fordele og begrænsninger</h2>
    <div class="pros-cons">
      <div class="pros">
        <h3>Fordele</h3>
        <p><strong>Privatliv</strong> – Minten kan ikke se din saldo, dine transaktioner eller hvem du handler med.</p>
        <p><strong>Hastighed</strong> – Transaktioner er øjeblikkelige, da de ikke kræver bekræftelse på blokkæden.</p>
        <p><strong>Lave gebyrer</strong> – Næsten gratis at sende og modtage.</p>
        <p><strong>Nem onboarding</strong> – Perfekt til små beløb, tips og mikrobetaling.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cons">
        <h3>Begrænsninger</h3>
        <p><strong>Tillid til minten</strong> – Dine bitcoin opbevares hos minten. Brug flere mints for at sprede risikoen.</p>
        <p><strong>Ikke til store beløb</strong> – Designet til daglige transaktioner, ikke til langsigtet opbevaring.</p>
        <p><strong>Enheds-afhængig</strong> – Tokens lever på din enhed, men Cashu har en gendannelsesfunktion med seed phrase.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="category-section">
    <h2>Lær mere</h2>
    <div class="links-grid">
      <a href="https://cashu.space/" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">Cashu.space</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">Officiel hjemmeside</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://docs.cashu.space/projects" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">Cashu Docs</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">Projekter & dokumentation</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://bitcoin.design/guide/how-it-works/ecash/cashu/" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="link-card-title">Bitcoin Design Guide</span>
        <span class="link-card-note">Visuel introduktion</span>
        <span class="link-card-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a href="#" class="back-to-top"> ↑ Tilbage til toppen </a>
</ResourcePageLayout>

<style>
  /* Navigation buttons */
  .nav-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md, 1rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .nav-btn {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 150px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--primary);
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--primary);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .nav-btn:hover {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  /* Intro */
  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-light, #ccc);
  }

  .intro p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Content sections */
  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-light, #ccc);
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md, 1rem);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm, 0.5rem);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(247, 147, 26, 0.2);
  }

  /* Steps */
  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(247, 147, 26, 0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .step-number {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    min-width: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .step-text {
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Pros and cons */
  .pros-cons {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .pros, .cons {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(247, 147, 26, 0.1);
  }

  .pros h3, .cons h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .pros p, .cons p {
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pros p:last-child, .cons p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Category sections */
  .category-section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .category-section h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm, 0.5rem);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm, 0.5rem);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(247, 147, 26, 0.2);
  }

  .section-desc {
    color: var(--text-light, #ccc);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md, 1rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Links grid */
  .links-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-md, 1rem);
  }

  .link-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(247, 147, 26, 0.15);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .link-card:hover {
    background: rgba(247, 147, 26, 0.08);
    border-color: var(--primary);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .link-card-title {
    color: var(--text-light, #ccc);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .link-card-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .link-card-arrow {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 567px) {
    .nav-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .links-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .pros-cons {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>